# Airbnb Clone — User Stories Documentation

## Overview
This directory contains the **User Stories** derived from the Airbnb Clone’s Use Case Diagram.  
Each story captures what the user wants to accomplish and why, providing a foundation for backend development and feature design.

---

## Contents
| File | Description |
|------|--------------|
| **user-stories.md** | Contains detailed user stories describing system interactions. |

---

## Purpose
User stories help translate the **Use Case Diagram** into functional requirements for developers.  
They guide implementation, testing, and validation of each system feature.

---

## Key Features Covered
1. User Registration and Authentication  
2. Property Listing (Host)  
3. Property Search and Booking (Guest)  
4. Secure Payment Processing  
5. Messaging Between Users  
6. Reviews and Ratings  
7. Admin Management  

